Hello! This is Kendrick Brinson, I'll be posting from Sun City, Arizona this week. Sun City is an age-restricted city of more than 40,000 retirees. When Del Webb opened Sun City in 1960, it was the first place of its kind. 
In this photo, my gracious host, Larry, picks grapefruit in his backyard. More to come soon!
